  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 255.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, as far as our living in southern France, Chateau la Hille, the reason I think it is so interesting is because when we left, we thought that the rest of the people perished because the Germans overran southern France and we know what happened to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must have been in total about 100 people and we knew of no survivors after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just-- when I came back to visit Chateau de la Hille as a young man, nobody knew what happened to any of them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just had disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It now turns out that Max Frank was alive, went to Germany after the war, and worked eventually in eastern Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why he didn't have contact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was in the eastern part of Germany and until the German reunification, he had very little communication with the West.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, after Germany was reunified, he started to look for his family because he considered all of the children of Chateau de la Hille part of his family.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was able to discover that most of them survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had escaped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had a reunion in Los Angeles several years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that reunion, they-- they found that there were three missing people, the Findling brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, my sister, who teaches in San Francisco, met a-- one of the congregation members and said, are you somehow related to the Findling brothers?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was your reunion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
